              "chord": "",
              "text": "Jesus breathed the Breath of Life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "From Him! From Him!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He only asked us to receive—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis not to think, but only breathe;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And it’s by this Breath that we experience Life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now wherever we may be"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There’s Air! There’s Air!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It surrounds, envelops us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It’s everywhere!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Available, so rich and free"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That we might live abundantly;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So brothers, sisters, breathe the Breath of Life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Just by calling on His Name,"
