          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord! O Lord!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ becomes the breath to us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord! O Lord!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We breathe His Name from deep within"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And breathe until we’re filled with Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And what a Breath this Jesus is to us!"
            }
